{"tid":147228,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Nintendo Switch貴價手掣有玄機　暗藏密碼答謝機迷","createTime":"2017-03-07T16:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T02:43:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3864e59d231019682616ba0f5dac4eecce1627ce","tid":147228,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/55ss10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F55ss10.jpg&h=8eb3c3bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知道有幾多人會在買Nintendo Switch的同時，會同時入手價錢幾達主機價錢4份1的Nintendo Switch Pro Controller呢？網站Polygon報道早前有網民留言發現Switch Pro Controller暗藏密碼，在右邊搖桿上方藏有「THX2 ALLGAMEFANS」的文字，按字面解讀是感謝所有遊戲粉絲。當然以Switch Pro Controller定價比PS4或Xbox One無線手掣都要高，任天堂肯暗地裏多謝粉絲支持，畀錢都畀得較順氣，如果大家已入手這個手掣的說，不妨睇下搵唔搵到這句「官方留言」。 <br />\n <br />\n資料來源：Polygon<br />\n <br />\n文：布偉倫<br />\n <br />\n2017果籽繼續認真知味。識買惜用。行以求知。好事多為。重修舊好。<br />\n緊貼果籽報道，即like：<a href=\"http://fb.me/AS.AppleDaily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2FAS.AppleDaily&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=67ea520e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.me/AS.AppleDaily</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/55ss11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F55ss11.jpg&h=4219c323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 用手指拉下右搖桿，會發現上方出現一串疑似文字。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/55ss12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F55ss12.jpg&h=cc96c4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 再放大睇，原來這段名字是「THX2 ALLGAMEFANS」，即感謝所有遊戲粉絲。"},{"pid":"5e4d0a980a5bc210105555331ab82dc74d61e440","tid":147228,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb6e60269ae351bbe5b15f39e403a82d2edb614","tid":147228,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}